OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fmoving westwards this evening, driven
OL,7,Fby strengthening winds from the east.
OL,8,FParticularly windy on coasts. Some
OL,9,Fspots of drizzle are possible. Staying
OL,10,Fmild overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRather cloudy to start, soon
OL,13,Fclearing to give lengthy sunny spells.
OL,14,FVery warm or hot in the west, cooler
OL,15,Fin the east and near coasts especially
OL,16,Fin the strong winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
