OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fdeveloping overnight during this
OL,7,Fperiod then burning back to coasts by
OL,8,Fday to give sunny spells. Perhaps an
OL,9,Fisolated thundery shower Monday and
OL,10,FWednesday. Very warm, perhaps hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
